title: Down on Trended Knee 1/17: Betty White, Karlie Kloss, Jonas Brothers, Ivy Park
itunes:title: Down on Trended Knee 1/17: Betty White, Karlie Kloss, Jonas Brothers, Ivy Park
description:
On this edition of Down on Trended Knee Miles and Laci discuss Betty White turning 98, Karlie Kloss saying she will - once again - not vote for Trump, Jo-Bros have a new video, and Beyoncé has released her Ivy Park collab with Adidas.
